    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- update to 6.2.1:
  * This release fixes some critical bugs reported/found after
    releasing 6.2.0
  * R6: fix valgrind error
  * tokeninfo: fix null pointer crash in tokenDelete function
  * Fixes segmentation fault when processing certain R6Class
    syntax patterns.
  * ada: Fix crash with `is` at EOF
  * Cxx: limit recursion when parsing too deep blocks
  * fixup! C++: Update the parser version to 2.2

- Initial package, build from git commit befcb88</comment>
